, it stole my bike</blockquote><br />\nGordon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8268a0955057c964bfde6bd5afaaa6a992da5ce4","tid":378248,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:15:39.000Z","msg":"Yahoo知識：<br />\n<br />\n簡簡單單要係屋企煎牛扒又好食的話,呢個一定係我暫時食過最好的.生粉加左係牛扒上面,煎的時候可以成為一個保護層,保護牛扒的肉油唔會流出來,而油就係用來令粉更易包實牛扒.煎的時候就算唔夠油都唔易&quot;痴&quot;底.這個方法是睇都市閒情,李錦聯師父教的.真係靠得住ga.肉汁唔流出來,牛扒自然就會更軟滑.比起出面的餐廳用鬆肉粉去掩而破壞肉味,這個方法真係一流.如果係唔落生粉同油,煎一次你就知差幾遠.所以大家如果真係想自己煎的話,不妨都試下呢個方法."},{"pid":"4027a1ef622665d4933db02695e51d2fc826ee67","tid":378248,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"首先要有royal級靚牛扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你買唔到 要專登訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64bdd5cb1e7593ea5209db8bd3785260112b6a9","tid":378248,"uid":23592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:37:22.000Z","msg":"The steak is darker than your future!"},{"pid":"2dc57a20e384fc04b40a76c39ec5d5703d326a39","tid":378248,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:45:42.000Z","msg":"手指公咁厚<br />\n諗住大火每面煎一分鐘 轉細火落牛油蒜頭每面30秒得唔得?"},{"pid":"fc9e2399c87d7bfaa848b14a2e37bd953b83818b","tid":378248,"uid":79036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5fdbecc22394807a0343f819e5419ea7ddca05","tid":378248,"uid":103558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:48:13.000Z","msg":"買太差既牛扒.就不如吾好煎<br />\n如果真係要用其他野醃塊牛扒.你拎塊牛去炒菜左都冇咁嬲.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e042ac62c0c0687122